                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://blog.sina.com.tw/d100vs/article.php?pbgid=30839&entryid=342476"><i>F. flavipuncatus</i> in the wild</a></li>
                        <li><a target="_blank" rel="noopener" rel="noreferrer" class="site-link" href="http://tw.myblog.yahoo.com/yore4/article?mid=17418&prev=17851&next=17370&l=f&fid=15&sc=1">Catching <i>F. flavipuncatus</i></a> in a paddy field</li>
                    </ul>     
